snippet.title: Java Modulus Tutorial - Learn Modulus in Java
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- Modulus is the remainder of division. Here are a few examples using modulus in java:

4/2 = 2 r 0
4%2 = 0

5/2 = 2 r 1
5%2 = 1

15/6 = 2 r 3
15%6 = 3

I hope this helps you make with modulus :) This is GREAT practice for modulus operator in java!

I hope you enjoyed this java modulus tutorial!
